high_descs: Turn around to reach the cabinet under the sidetable.
Pick up the plate from the cabinet.
Turn right and head down the passage on the right and reach the bathroom on the left to reach the sink.
Wash the plate in the sink and take the plate out.
Turn around to exit the bathroom and reach the sidetable across the room.
Put the plate on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed Plate on the SideTable.

high_descs: Turn around to the left, move forward, and turn right to the sidetable.
Take the plate from the TV cupboard.
Turn right, move forward, then turn right again and move forward. Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward, turn left, move forward and turn left again to the sink.
Place the plate in the sink, tap the water to clean the plate, and take the plate out.
Turn left, move forward, turn right, move forward. Turn left, move forward and turn right to the sidetable.
Place the plate on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned plate on the SideTable from the TV SideTable.

high_descs:
Turn right go straight turn left go to the side table

Take back in the plate
